title: Reach
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A figure with this keyword may perform [img[Melee Attack.png]] (melee) attacks that target figures or objects up to 2 spaces away.

* The attacking figure must have line of sight to the target in order to make this attack.
* An attack with Reach does not require Accuracy. 

